: null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011373, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O my Ultimate Sanctuary when troubles surround me! O my Last Hope when difficulties trouble me! Unto Thee I turn to, before Thee I stand to get help, with Thee I take refuge, except Thee there is no refuge; I do not seek joy after sorrow from anyone save Thee, O come to my help and free me from cares O He who accept even the smallest (efforts) but excuses from restrictions, accept whatever little there is and release from hardships frequently, verily Thou art Oft-forgiving, Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay museebat mein meri panah-gah (hifaazat ki jagah), ay sakhti mein mere fariyaad-ras (fariyaad soonne waala). Dara huwa Tere paas aaya hu aur Tujh se fariyaad karta hu, Teri taraf daudta hu, Tere gair ki panah nahi leta aur na hi Tere siwa kisi se kasha-ish (halle mushkilaat) ka taalib hu, pas meri fariyaad soon aur kasha-ish ataa kar (meri mushkilaat aasaan farma). Ay woh jo thoda amal qabool karta hai aur bohot se gunaho’n ko maaf karta hai, mujh se bhi thoda amal qabool farma aur bohot se gunaho’n ko maaf farma, be-shak Tu hi bohot bakhsh ne waala maher-baan hai.", "Urdu": "اے مصیبت میں میری پناہ گاہ اے سختی میں میرے فریادرس ڈرا ہوا تیرے پاس آیا ہوں اور تجھ سے فریاد کرتا ہوں تیری طرف دوڑا ہوں اور تیرے غیر کی پناہ نہیں لیتا تیرے سوا کسی سے کشائش وآسائش کا طالب نہیں ہوں پس میری فریاد سن اور کشائش وآسائش عطا کر اے وہ جو تھوڑا عمل قبول کرتا ہے اور بہت سے گناہ معاف کرتا ہے مجھ سے بھی تھوڑا عمل قبول فرما اور بہت سے گناہوں کو معاف کردے بے شک تو ہی بہت بخشنے والا مہربان ہے۔", "RArabic": "YAA MAFZA-EE’ I’NDA KURBA-TEE WA YAA GHAW-SEE I’NDA SHIDDA-TEE ILAIY-KA FAZE’TO WA BE-KASTA GHAS-TO WA BE-KA LUZTO LAA ALOO-ZO BE-SEWAA-KA WA LAA ATLO-BUL FARAJA ILLAA MINKA FA-A-GHIS-NEE WA FARRIJ A’NNEE YAA MAIY-YAQBA-LUL YASEERA WA YA’FOO A’NNAL KASEERA IQ-BAL MINNAL YASEERA WA’FO A’NNIL KASEERA INNA-KA ANTAL GHAFOO-RUR RAHEEMO.", "ArabicText1": "یَامَفْزَعِیْ عِنْدَ کُرْبَتِیْ وَیَا غَوْثِیْ عِنْدَ شِدَّتِیْ اِلَیْکَ فَزِعْتُ وَبِکَ اسْتَغَثْتُ وَبِکَ لُذْتُ لَااَلُوْذُبِسِوَاکَ وَلَااَطْلُبُ الْفَرَجَ اِلَّامِنْکَ فَاَغِثْنِیْ وَفَرِّجْ عَنِّیْ یَامَنْ یَّقْبَلُ الْیَسِیْرَ وَیَعْفُوْ عَنَّ الْکَثِیْرَ اِقْبَلْ مِنَّی الْیَسِیْرَ وَاعْفُ عَنِّی الْکَثِیْرَ اِنَّکَ اَنْتَ الْغَفُوْرُالرَّحِیْمُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011372, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah I ask for faith which gives joy, satisfaction and confidence to my heart till I am positively aware that I will not have my fill unless it has been approved for me, and happiness will agree with me only whereby justly and fairly distributed, O the Most Merciful. O my “means” in my troubles! O my companion in my difficulties! O my guardian in my happiness! O the ultimate of my inclinations! Thou covers up my shortcomings, affords security in the event of crisis and fearful disasters, therefore, overlook my transgressions, O the Most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Mai Tujh se aise imaan ka sawaali hu jo mere dil mein jama rahe aur aisa yaqeen keh jis se mai yeh samajh ne lagu keh mujhe nahi pohonchega magar jo Tu ne meri qismat mein likkha hai, aur mujhe us zindagi par raazi o khush rakh jo Tu ne mujhe di hai. Ay sab se ziyadah rahem karne waale, ay museebat mein mere sarmaya (ummeed), ay sakhti mein mere saathi, ay neymat mein mere sarprast, aur ay meri chaahat ke markaz. Tu mere aiybo’n (galtiyo’n) ka chhupa ne waala, khouf mein amn dene waala, aur meri galtiya’n maaf karne waala hai. Pas meri khataaye’n bakhsh de ay sab se ziyadah rahem karne waale.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! میں تجھ سے ایسے ایمان کا سوالی ہوں جو میرے دل میں جما رہے اور ایسا یقین کہ جس سے میں یہ سمجھنے لگوں کہ مجھے وہی پہنچے گا جو تو نے میرے لئے لکھا ہے اور مجھے اس زندگی پر شاد رکھ جو تو نے مجھے دی ہے اے سب سے زیادہ رحم کرنے والے اے مصیبت میں میرے سرمایہ اے سختی میں میرے ساتھی اے نعمت میں میرے سرپرست اور اے میری چاہت کے مرکز تو میرے عیبوں کا چھپانے والا خوف میں امان دینے والا اور میری غلطیاں معاف کرنے والا ہے پس میری خطائیں بخش دے اے سب سے زیادہ رحم کرنے والے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNEE AS-ALOKA EEMAA-NAN TOBAA-SHERO BEHI QALBEE WA YAQEE-NAN SAADE-QAN HATTAA A’LAMO ANNA-HU LANY-YOSEE-BANEE ILLAA MAA KATAB-TA LEE WA RAZZE-NEE MENAL A’IY-SHE BE-MAA QASAM-TALEE YAA AR-HAMAR RAAHE-MEENA YAA U’DDA-TEE FEE KURBA-TEE WA YAA SAAHE-BEE FEE SHIDDA-TEE WA YAA WALIYYEE FEE NE’MATEE WA YAA GHAAYA-TEE FEE RAGHA-BATEE ANTAS SAATERO A’W-RATEE WAL AA-MENO RAW-A’TEE WAL MOQEE-LO A’SRA-TEE FAGH-FIR-LEE KHATEE-A-TEE YAA AR-HAMAR RAAHE-MEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰھُمَّ اِنِّیْ اَسْئَلُکَ اِیْمَانًا تُبَاشِرُ بِہٖ قَلْبِیْ وَیَقِیْنًا صَادِقًاحَتّٰی اَعْلَمُ اَنَّہٗ لَنْ یُّصِیْبَنِیْ اِلَّا مَاکَتَبْتَ لِیْ وَرَضِّنِیْ مِنَ الْعَیْشِ بِمَا قَسَمْتَ لِیْ یَااَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِیْنَ یَاعُدَّتِیْ فِیْ کُرْبَتِیْ وَیَا صَاحِبِیْ فِیْ شِدَّتِیْ وَیَا وَلِیّٖ فِیْ نِعْمَتِیْ وَیَا غَایَتِیْ فِیْ رَغَبَتِیْ اَنْتَ السَّاتِرُ عَوْرَتِیْ وَالْاٰمِنُ رَوْعَتِیْ وَالْمُقِیْلُ عَثْرَتِیْ فَاغْفِرْلِیْ خَطِیْئَتِیْ یَااَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": nul